Juncker Says ‘Positively Hopeful’ on Future EFSF Leveraging

-- B y   J o n a t h a n   S t e a r n s
-- 
2011-10-03T22:31:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/juncker-says-positively-hopeful-on-future-efsf-leveraging.html
Luxembourg’s  Jean-Claude Juncker , who
leads the group of euro-area finance ministers, said he’s
“positively hopeful” on future leveraging of the region’s
temporary rescue fund. He spoke to reporters in Luxembourg
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jonathan Stearns in Luxembourg at 
